responseText: NSLOCTEXT("", "3AC680954B1216E370F746BD0DB42771", "I am just Wun. Sodbottoms help Dargulls when evils fall from sky. Farmers teach Sodbottoms. We learn some words. Then blood gobbers come. Kills farmers and traps Sodbottoms. They mad. They bleed Sodbottoms on big rock from sky.")
